sumvalue.append(3500)

            x=sumvalue,
            y=['전달', 'QCA', '저장', '', '1차년도 목표', '2차년도 목표', '과제 최종 목표'],

2. 주별 작업 진행 현황 (누적)¶

In [50]:
weekly_save = go.Bar(x=data_weekly_cumsum.index, y=data_weekly_cumsum['save'], name='저장')

weekly_QCA = go.Bar(x=data_weekly_cumsum.index, y=data_weekly_cumsum['QCA'], name='QCA')

weekly_delivered = go.Bar(x=data_weekly_cumsum.index, y=data_weekly_cumsum['delivered'], name='전달')

weekly_chart = [weekly_save, weekly_QCA, weekly_delivered]
layout = go.Layout(barmode=weekly_chart)
fig = go.Figure(data=weekly_chart, layout=layout)
iplot(fig, filename='grouped-bar')

### input block hiding (click button)

HTML('''<script>
code_show=true; 
function code_toggle() {
 if (code_show){
 $('div.input').hide();
 } else {
 $('div.input').show();
 }
 code_show = !code_show
} 
$( document ).ready(code_toggle);
</script>
<form action="javascript:code_toggle()"><input type="submit" value="Click here to toggle on/off the raw code."></form>
''')
